text: The Distinguished Gentleman is a 1992 American political comedy movie directed by Jonathan Lynn and starring Eddie Murphy, Lane Smith, Sheryl Lee Ralph, Joe Don Baker, Victoria Rowell, Grant Shaud, Kevin McCarthy, Charles S. Dutton. It was distributed by Buena Vista Pictures Distribution. == Other websites == * * * Category:1992 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Political movies Category:Movies directed by Jonathan Lynn
title: The Distinguished Gentleman
